reports.summary: The bassline is wrong, flea smashes the open D string,not 5th fret from A string.Although its the same note,its easier to play that way.The second mistake I noticed is in the bassline again.It goes like 5 7 5 7 5 7 5 5 7 on the g string but instead its all 7's.The intro is correct tho.
